snippet.title: Squirreled Away - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam now!  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2977620/Squirreled_Away/

Be the squirrel. Scurry through gardens, up trees, and leap limb to limb in this craft and thrive parklife adventure. Explore solo or with up to three squirrel buddies in co-op. Meet and help other residents and collect bits here and there to build and decorate your dream treehouse.
